## Goal

Harden database query performance and prevent Full Table Scans under heavy project graph volumes.

## Requirements

- Create a compound index on `nodes`: `{project_id: 1, type: 1}`.
- Create single-field indexes on `edges`: `{project_id: 1}`.
- Create single-field indexes on `snapshots`: `{project_id: 1}`.

